{"type": "article", "id": 25441, "title": "光笼灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-04-14T06:59:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 42, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140252UXlzunbOcpYvsiDL.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这是造作和瑞典设计工作室 NOTE 再次合作推出的灯具，用金属网制成双层的球形结构。网格纹路会因为球体本身产生疏密的变化，加上两层大小网格重叠和灯泡发散的光线影响，增加更多的层次，非常细腻。如果将这盏灯旋转过来，灯泡所在的小圈金属网格则会更加明亮，很轻盈。有黄、红、黑三种颜色旋转，售价 909 元，<a href=\"http://zaozuo.com/item/300098\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"medium-insert-active com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140250UnVyeIcuORZx0Xr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.67222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140250MQmKjqvFWbItTyef.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.64907407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140251wJKuMB87TySVZe6t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.55740741\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140251N1M8E7mI2yzJa9TS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.32592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}